data.description: This exquisite property is situated in the highly coveted Alamo Ranch area, renowned for its remarkable family-friendly environment and exceptional educational institutions. The house boasts an expansive open living area, adorned with recently installed new flooring, offering a serene and comfortable living experience. Well maintained with a new furnace (2023), this residence features four spacious bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and a versatile loft/game room. The opportunity to own this move-in ready property should not be missed.  Schedule an appointment today to witness its charm and comfortable home.
